---
title: BBQ & Cherry-Glazed Beef Meatballs with Potato Wedges & Creamy Slaw
description: Round out the warmer months with spectacular beef meatballs, drizzled with a sticky-sweet cherry and BBQ glaze. And
for the real ‘cherry‘ on top, we’ve added wedges and a creamy apple slaw for crunch and depth of flavour to boot!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64c5ee1b459aba500a5fae73-c028e99e.jpeg
